name: fhf-linkedlist
description: The fhf-linkedlist library is a high-performance JavaScript implementation of a linked list, leveraging WebAssembly for efficient memory management and fast execution. It provides an easy-to-use API for common linked list operations such as appending, pushing, deleting, and reversing nodes. Designed for developers needing optimal performance in their web applications, fhf-linkedlist seamlessly integrates with WebAssembly, offering a robust solution for handling dynamic data structures.
author: Mahdi Amari
